snippet.title: A new trailer for Aveliana made for The Escapist!
snippet.description:
Aveliana had the opportunity to be showcased at The Escapist game showcase event (fall edition) this year! This was an incredible event in which I had the chance to be interviewed!

You can find The Escapist channel here:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqg5FCR7NrpvlBWMXdt-5Vg
